      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 203,
      "message": "Adding the getDefinedName() and getDefinedVersion() to the PfNameVersion interface allows us to ahve the default value of a name and version on a ToscaEntity as PfKey.NULL_KEY_NAME and PfKey.NULL_KEY_VERSION rather than Java \"null\" when we read concepts in from JSON or YAML. THis makes the processing much easier as we don't have to worry about nulls existing.\n\nThe getDefinedName() and getDefinedVersion() methods return Java \"null\" if the name or version is not defined, ie is \"null\" of the PfKey interpretation of null.",
